{"type": "article", "id": 36424, "title": "梅西百货关店63家，以及，LEGO街景系列推出十周年版 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-05T03:19:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1029, "name": "Lego"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 1581, "name": "Chloe"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 2636, "name": "Swatch"}, {"id": 3289, "name": "梅西百货"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170105100507oIWmPDtTJqu5aEXZ.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2017/01/04/macys-holiday-season-closings/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国梅西百货将在今年春天大幅度关店并裁员</b></a> | 周三，梅西宣布它将在这个春天关闭 63 家店铺，裁员近 1000 人。梅西在去年十一月和十二月业绩下降了 2.1%，股票下跌了近 10%，业绩持续低迷不振，是梅西关店和裁员的主要原因。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/coach-names-new-cfo-1483535721\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Coach 任命新的 CFO</b></a> | Kevin Wills 将成为 Coach 的新任 CFO，此前，他在咨询公司 AlixPartners 担任 CFO。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2017/01/clare-waight-keller-out-chloe\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>CHLOÉ 要换创意总监</b></a> | 在前任创意总监 Clare Waight Keller 离职之后，Ramsay-Levi 将成为 CHLOÉ 的创意总监。Ramsay-Levi 在此之前担任 Louis Vuitton 的高级创意总监。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/10-lego-10255-assembly-square\" rel=\"nofollow\">LEGO 街景系列推出十周年版本</a>。LEGO 街景系列自从 2007 年推出以来，就备受追捧。日前，LEGO 公布了十周年版本 10255 Assembly Square，它由 4002 块 LEGO 组成，比之前的款式更宏伟。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102124CNtzY2xVJqMpU3Xo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102124CFsS9Jh6Ba4we8Eg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701051021243yv4DfVdZbFoSEIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102125K8VyhALJ97FNjGpS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102134DYafcm08J7LXCNzW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102134i9ldXeWJB7G5p4x0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/jordan-4-super-nintendo-custom\" rel=\"nofollow\">球鞋定制专家 Freaker Sneaks，设计了一款以任天堂游戏机为灵感的 Jordan 4</a>，还挺有趣的，现在可由 <a href=\"http://freakersneaks.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Freaker Sneaks</a> 官网进行预订。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102155lJEuFmKMqev75Nbc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676758\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102202MGuqhkiRY1gmFd2U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102207ksAEjB89WqRPoy1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666297\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/swatch-rocking-rooster\" rel=\"nofollow\">Swatch 推出鸡年特别款手表</a>。其配色以中国传统的金色和红色为主，并融入了特色纺织图案和剪纸艺术，售价为 620 人民币。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102215uBbxJnAi4YtfgIzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102222AxTtXo1LkKyHNQDq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102222TKZOAk5gG2VYPiN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102222wfmoQzecGPJsMaOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/adidas-originals-by-white-mountaineering-2017-spring-summer-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 与日本品牌 White Mountaineering 合作</a>，发布 2017 春夏系列 lookbook。该系列包括运动外套、风衣、Logo T-Shirt、卫衣、运动裤及短裤等多款单品，将在本月登陆 adidas Originals 指定店铺，并于 3 月发布第二波新品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102232H1RQE8CsGUzJl4tv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102232cESyW5jJgihOQCob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102234jIwYOoSEdvReZn2Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102234IOVtsGpLyEMojXgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102234gbtHqjDiL2WpSkE5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102234BDdExfkeguphOy7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102240B1AHoqvZY57f8Wb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/photographer-june-young-lim-like-water-01-04-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">在摄影师 June Young Lim 的镜头下，“水”成了主角</a>。他拍摄了一个名为 like water 的系列照片，以纽约都市街头为背景，记录下了水的运动瞬间，这种动静结合呈现出别样的美感。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701051022526iCJXkZqDgrOUQGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102306faGjkSQYAVhd7MTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102306wjOyde972VFi5k8T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701051023152f6xdp5jqSz8wT4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102328iZyWFX2URlvgErIu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.367971\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170105102328d7g4OQIDGAFZM2WP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.348411\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/10-lego-10255-assembly-square\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}